# Reference accessed: 2026-05-31 via gh api.
#
# ttc-converter CLI surface (decoded source-direct):
#   -? / -h / --help        Show help (MULTI-CHAR-LIST short)
#   -i FILE / --input FILE  Input file name
#   -o FILE / --output FILE Output file name
#   --ttc                   TTC format
#   --ttm                   TTM format
#   --erase-fc              Do not write FC in JSON
#   --erase-mn              Do not write MN indexes in JSON
